                    Drop us an 
                    <a 
                        href="mailto:hey@datagrove.com" 
                        target="_blank"
                        class="text-accent"
                    >email</a>
                </h3>

                <svg 
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" 
                    width="32" 
                    height="32" 
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    class="pl-1"
